OL,7,FITV News Central Correspondent Rajiv
OL,8,FPopat has the latest on the review
OL,9,Finto the Leicester riots
OL,11,FPeople in Leicester who were impacted
OL,12,Fby are being asked to share their
OL,13,Fviews and experiences as part of an
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,FThe unrest was sparked by tensions
OL,17,Fbetween Muslim and Hindu communities
OL,18,Fin August and September 2022.
