OL,7,FDays of broke out following an India v
OL,8,FPakistan cricket match, which resulted
OL,9,Fin more than 60 arrests.
OL,11,FThe Independent Leicester Review Panel
OL,12,Fis conducting an investigation into
OL,13,Fthe violence, which aims to shed light
OL,14,Fon why it started and what lessons can
OL,15,Fbe learned.
OL,17,FThe government-backed review is being
OL,18,Fled by former Labour MP Ian Austin,
OL,19,Fwho now wants the public to help with
OL,20,Fthe inquiry.
