OL,7,FMr Austin said: "We've heard from
OL,8,Fhundreds of local people, we've met
OL,9,Flots of local councillors, community
OL,10,Fgroups and local voluntary and faith
OL,11,Forganisations.
OL,13,F"We want to make sure that everyone in
OL,14,FLeicester who has a view on this has
OL,15,Fthe opportunity to make sure their
OL,16,Fviews are being taken into
OL,17,Fconsideration."
OL,19,FThe inquiry will also hear from a
OL,20,Frange of individuals and organisations
OL,21,Fover the next four weeks.
