OL,7,FIn June 2023, the Muslim Council of
OL,8,FBritain (MCB) expressed its over the
OL,9,Fappointment of Mr Austin to lead the
OL,10,Freview.
OL,12,FThe Council said: "The appointment of
OL,13,FLord Austin, given his divisive record
OL,14,Fand the serious allegations of
OL,15,FIslamophobia against him, has created
OL,16,Fdeep apprehension among Muslims and
OL,17,Fother communities in Leicester."
