OL,7,FAt the time, a DLUHC spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are confident that this
OL,9,Fthorough, independent review will
OL,10,Fstrengthen community cohesion in
OL,11,FLeicester - a city with a proud
OL,12,Fhistory of tolerance and diversity."
OL,14,FThe deadline for the public to submit
OL,15,Ftheir views on the government website
OL,16,Fis Tuesday 4 June.
OL,18,FThe findings of the review are due to
OL,19,Fbe published in October.
